name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text: I cosponsored the Enhanced Background Checks Act to revise background check requirements applicable to proposed firearm transfers from a federal firearms licensee to an unlicensed person.

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text: I cosponsored the Extreme Risk Protection Order Act to address red flag laws, generally to allow law enforcement officers or family members to petition a court for a temporary order that prohibits an at-risk individual from purchasing and possessing firearms.

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text:

I twice cosponsored the Keep Americans Safe Act to establish a new criminal offense for the sale of a large capacity ammunition feeding device.

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text:
I twice cosponsored the Untraceable Firearms Act to ban the manufacture, sale, transfer, purchase, or receipt of guns that lack a unique serial number (“ghost guns”).

I cosponsored Ethan's Law to establish a framework to regulate the storage of firearms on residential premises.

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text: I twice cosponsored the Public Safety and Second Amendment Rights Protection Act to require states to implement plans to improve the submission of mental health and criminal history records to the national instant criminal background check system.

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦

I cosponsored Jaime’s Law to establish background check requirements for the sale and transfer of ammunition.

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text:
I cosponsored the Gun Violence Restraining Order Act to ban firearm sales to a person subject to a court-issued gun violence prevention order.

I cosponsored the Disarm Hate Act to prevent a person convicted of a hate crime from obtaining a firearm.

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text:

name: Congressman Donald Norcross 🇺🇸🇺🇦
tweet_text:
